<div class="heading">
<h1><span>Who I Am</span></h1>
</div>
<p>Hello.</p>
<p>My name's <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610081504" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;">Nagiros</a></span>, although I also use Nagi for short. I use she/they pronouns, and I'm currently 19. I'm a believer in music and emotion. I've got a lot to learn about this site and life in general.</p>
<p>I review articles posted to the Idea and Draft forums, as well as creating my own SCPs, tales, and GOI Formats — you may see me around sometimes, and I'm always happy to help if you want some eyes on a draft.</p>
<p>I'm most well-known for making a lot of contributions to the <a href="/site-17-hub">Site-17 Deepwell Catalog</a> and creating/maintaining the <a href="/esoteric-classes-complete-list">Comprehensive List of Esoteric Classes</a>. I have aspirations of doing more — I want to be prolific and have a formidable backlog of content I can be proud of. I want to inspire others.</p>
<p>We'll see.</p>
